text: The Pirate Party () is a small political party in Morocco which was founded in 2011. It is one of the first Pirate parties in the African continent, second to the Tunisian Pirate Party. The party is formed by several youth activists and isn't recognised yet by the Moroccan law. == References == == External links == * Official website Category:Pirate parties Category:Political parties in Morocco
title: Pirate Party of Morocco
